---
title: Asian Crumbed Pork & Soy Veggies with Ginger Rice & Sesame Dressing
description: This pork schnitzel has a fun Asian twist, with sesame seeds mixed right into the golden crumb. Serve it atop fragrant ginger rice and savoury soy veggies, with a drizzle of sesame dressing to pull it all together. Go on, grab a fork and dig right in!
